<p><strong>Scenario — Fashion browse abandonment:</strong> Module: hero SKU image, Yotpo fit review quote, two-tap CTA, single related product. No six-grid. Dark mode tested. Map this scenario to your vertical guide at /for if category-specific suppressions apply (Recharge tags, wholesale accounts, gift buyers).</p>
<p><strong>Scenario — Beauty replenishment:</strong> SKU image, usage reminder copy block, subscription status badge if Recharge synced, one-tap reorder button deep-linked to cart. Map this scenario to your vertical guide at /for if category-specific suppressions apply (Recharge tags, wholesale accounts, gift buyers).</p>
